00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,640
 Zašto ja živim?

759
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:08,820
 Stvarno čiji je svijet?

760
00:25:09,540 --> 00:25:10,960
 Imali li itko na ovoj zemlji

761
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,700
 danas od šest milijardi ljudi?

762
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,600
 Pokraj svih visokih stručnjaka

763
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:15,400
 kojima se klanjamo.

764
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,280
 Imali li itko

765
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:17,740
 tko zna zašto mi tu živimo?

766
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:18,880
 Gdje smo mi to?

767
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,540
 Dokle ćemo tu biti?

768
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:23,740
 Imali li itko

769
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,760
 tko zna

770
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,760
 kod su danas

771
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:26,620
 sto tisuća ljudi

772
00:25:26,620 --> 00:25:27,320
 koji su umrli?

773
00:25:27,320 --> 00:25:28,420
 Gdje su ti ljudi?

774
00:25:28,420 --> 00:25:31,660
 Zašto je čovjek

775
00:25:31,660 --> 00:25:32,400
 tako zločist?

776
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:36,080
 Imali li itko tko zna?

777
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:38,120
 Samo promisli.

778
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:40,040
 Jedan može pogleda svoju ruku.

779
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,500
 Pa pogleda ljude

780
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,160
 i pogleda

781
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,700
 gle, on ih je stvorio.

782
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:44,360
 I sad ti ćeš

783
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:45,320
 o, pa ti si tu.

784
00:25:45,320 --> 00:25:49,900
 I tad mu se duboko pokloni

785
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:50,800
 i kaže prijatelju

786
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:52,640
 Bože moj, reci mi

787
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:53,640
 što da radi.

788
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:55,840
 Čim tako gledaš

789
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:57,500
 ti si uspeo na razinu duha

790
00:25:57,500 --> 00:25:59,260
 ti si otvorio oči duše

791
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:00,200
 i ti Boga vidiš

792
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:00,840
 više ni problem.

793
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:01,980
 Tako lijepo bići

794
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:02,860
 s Isusom, vjerujte me.

795
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:03,480
 Prehlasno.

796
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:04,920
 Ja bih samo htio jedno

797
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,760
 da doćete do toga.

798
00:26:05,760 --> 00:26:07,640
 A vi doćete da slušate predavanja

799
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,760
 a ja nisam za to ovdje došao.

800
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:10,020
 Oopće nisam ga spremao danas.

801
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:11,740
 Ja bih htio da vi se usretne

802
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:12,220
 da vidite Isusa.

803
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:12,660
 Jer znam

804
00:26:12,660 --> 00:26:14,120
 kad njega se usretnete

805
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,220
 život postaje lud,

806
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,160
 fascinantan.

807
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:17,580
 Tad je sve lijepo biti.

808
00:26:17,580 --> 00:26:19,960
 I sve lijepo raditi.

809
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,420
 I ništa više ni teško.

810
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,660
 I uvek ćeš uspjeti.

811
00:26:22,660 --> 00:26:26,700
 Znate da je temeljna stvar,

812
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:28,280
 temeljna poluga u životu.

813
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:30,720
 Biti prijatelj s Bogom.

814
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:31,680
 Sve drugo je nevažno.

815
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:35,040
 Sa šefom čitavog svemira

816
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:35,800
 doći u kontakt.

817
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,360
 Probajte još jednom.

818
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:41,980
 Možda ipak uspijete.

819
00:26:41,980 --> 00:26:45,060
 Ako ne ićemo doma.

820
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:48,000
 Probajte.

821
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,280
 Potrudite se samo.

822
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:50,500
 Isplati se, kaže vam.

823
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:55,500
 Zanimljivo je gledat vas.

824
00:26:55,500 --> 00:26:56,820
 Svi koji gledate u ruke,

825
00:26:56,820 --> 00:26:58,580
 vidi se na vam da ste se promijenili

826
00:26:58,580 --> 00:27:00,800
 i da zaista ste shvatili

827
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:03,600
 da je tu nešto vidljivi znak

828
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,800
 Božeg prisutnosti.

829
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,040
 Oni koji ne dalje su zabrnuti

830
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:07,480
 i gledaju

831
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,920
 i razmišljaju.

832
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,900
 Svati da se Boga

833
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,620
 ne dohvaća razmišljanjem.

834
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:14,300
 Razmišljanjem je dohvaćaš

835
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,560
 samo svoju mislu,

836
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:16,320
 ali ne Boga.

837
00:27:16,320 --> 00:27:17,320
 Bog nije mislu.

838
00:27:17,320 --> 00:27:19,520
 I nije u mislima.

839
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:21,420
 Nego upravo u tom

840
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:23,140
 duh tvoj intuicijski.

841
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,820
 Duh gleda u trenutku.

842
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:26,880
 Intuicijski prepoznaje tu je.

843
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,200
 I tad si sretan.

844
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:32,760
 Da Boga se ne dolazi razmišljanjem.

845
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:33,200
 Svati.

846
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,520
 Samo vidiš.

847
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:38,540
 Uhvatiš gospodina.

848
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:43,720
 Idemo sada još jedan korak do Boga.

849
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:46,800
 Naši susreti četvrtkom služa

850
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:48,540
 upravo da bismo susreli Boga.

851
00:27:48,540 --> 00:27:51,080
 Da bi se s njime živjeli.

852
00:27:51,080 --> 00:27:54,060
 Da bi se ga vidjeli, čuli, doživjeli.

853
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:58,240
 I zato ovo prvo, prvi način

854
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:59,860
 kako ćeš Boga prepoznati.

855
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:02,120
 Drugo, kako ćeš Boga prepoznati?

856
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:05,020
 Kad nekome oprostiš

857
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,280
 što te je povrijedio,

858
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:08,400
 ako mu oprostiš

859
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,740
 i pokuša čitavim slice reći

860
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:10,740
 opraštam ti.

861
00:28:10,740 --> 00:28:12,480
 Ne moraš ići k njemu,

862
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,760
 nego samo u sebi reći

863
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:15,300
 opraštam ti, razumijem te,

864
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:16,800
 ne dam da me zlo zahvati

865
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:17,680
 iz tebe.

866
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,780
 Opraštam ti.

867
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:21,420
 To ćeš osjetiti isto blizinu Božu.

868
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:24,780
 Ili ako se odlučiš

869
00:28:24,780 --> 00:28:26,640
 da ćeš biti dobar.

870
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,140
 Ako kažeš

871
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,280
 žao mi je što sam dosad bio zločest

872
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:30,580
 i zao što sam psovao,

873
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:31,820
 ogovarao, ljenčario,

874
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,120
 bludničio,

875
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,380
 krao i tako dalje.

876
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:35,100
 Žao mi je.

877
00:28:35,100 --> 00:28:36,640
 Ako se odlučiš od sad,

878
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,960
 želim biti drugačiji.

879
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:38,980
 Želim biti pošten,

880
00:28:38,980 --> 00:28:40,640
 čestit, pravedan čovjek.

881
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:43,140
 Čim te okažeš,

882
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:45,000
 Boga ćeš odmah susresti.

883
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:45,480
 Zašto?

884
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,480
 Jer činiti grijeh

885
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,160
 znači

886
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:50,800
 uništavati svoje sposobnosti.

887
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,380
 Vi znate da

888
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:54,180
 neurologija tako jasno kaže,

889
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:55,960
 čim rekneš negativnu riječ,

890
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:58,380
 ti si već uništio nekoliko stanica svoga mozga.

891
00:28:58,380 --> 00:29:00,520
 I nesposoban si vidjeti stvari.

892
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:05,540
 Kad se opredjeluješ za dobro,

893
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,460
 za pozitivno,

894
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,100
 za čestito,

895
00:29:07,100 --> 00:29:08,960
 mozak se rehabilitira.

896
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:12,200
 Čak i onaj dio mozga

897
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,420
 koji si uništio drogom,

898
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,120
 alkoholom

899
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,440
 i koji je čim drugim.

900
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:18,080
 I budući dakle,

901
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:19,000
 da je Bog uvijek

902
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,020
 apsolutno biće,

903
00:29:20,020 --> 00:29:20,360
 zato,

904
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:22,340
 čim se opredjeluješ za dobro,

905
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,700
 tada i tvoj mozak,

906
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:25,040
 i sve tvoje sposobnosti su

907
00:29:25,040 --> 00:29:26,580
 izvrsne,

908
00:29:26,580 --> 00:29:27,220
 vrsne,

909
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:28,140
 dakle vrhunske,

910
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:29,380
 i zato možeš Boga sresti.

911
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:30,560
 Ako si u zlu,

912
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:32,420
 tada su tvoje sposobnosti minimalne.

913
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,200
 To ti je kao da

914
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,520
 jedva vidiš ovako,

915
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,560
 li ima svijetla?

916
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:36,180
 Ne ima.

917
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,160
 To ti je kad činiš grije.

918
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,860
 Tebi zapravo su zatvorene oči,

919
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:41,900
 uništen pogled

920
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:42,960
 i ne možeš ništa vidjeti.

921
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:47,020
 A čim se opredjeluješ za dobro,

922
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:47,280
 jedan puta,

923
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:48,020
 bu, ho.

924
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:51,820
 Jedan puta vidiš tamo,

925
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:52,740
 kao na onoj slici,

926
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,840
 kako to Michelangelo kraso

927
00:29:54,840 --> 00:29:56,720
 napravio u kapeli Sistini,

928
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,420
 kako Bog pruža svoj prs,

929
00:29:58,420 --> 00:29:59,240
 a ti polako svoj,

930
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,100
 pa se još pružaš, pružaš.

931
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:01,020
 A Isus kaže,

932
00:30:01,020 --> 00:30:02,320
 di još malo se odreci zla.

933
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:03,600
 Di još malo.

934
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:04,880
 I da odirnete se.

935
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,760
 A to je lijepo.

936
00:30:07,460 --> 00:30:09,120
 Znate kada je ljubav najdraža,

937
00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:10,400
 najsilovitija?

938
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:12,960
 Kada svako volite,

939
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:13,940
 mladići djevoke,

940
00:30:13,940 --> 00:30:15,620
 ili kada si krad mami,

941
00:30:15,620 --> 00:30:16,600
 ili neko ko te voli.

942
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:17,900
 I sam ovako malo,

943
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:20,180
 malim prstem dodirneš njegov mali prst.

944
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:21,320
 Što je to ljubav?

945
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,420
 Kada nešto plane od tebe,

946
00:30:23,420 --> 00:30:24,220
 silovito.

947
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:26,740
 Ono kad ga zagriješ,

948
00:30:26,740 --> 00:30:27,500
 poljiveš, nije to.

949
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:28,700
 Onda kada sve unišiš nekako.

950
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:29,760
 Boli je te leža,

951
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:30,240
 boli grlo,

952
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,880
 boli te vrat,

953
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,540
 boli ruke.

954
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:36,240
 Ali ono malo nježno to plane.

955
00:30:36,340 --> 00:30:37,640
 čitava duša plane.

956
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,400
 To je upravo to.

957
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,380
 To je Michelangelo napravio.

958
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:43,520
 S ono je kratko dodirno.

959
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:48,280
 I to je duhovna dimenzija, vidite.

960
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:51,120
 Boga ne treba da čvrsto uzmiš,

961
00:30:51,120 --> 00:30:52,560
 pa zgrabiš, pa uništiš sve.

962
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:53,980
 Gdje si Isuse?

963
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:54,640
 On kaže,

964
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,280
 bježmo, dečke, idu cure.

965
00:30:57,620 --> 00:30:58,620
 Bježmo odavde,

966
00:30:58,620 --> 00:30:59,620
 oče moju ugraviti.

967
00:30:59,620 --> 00:31:01,540
 Nego kada ona izdaleka nježno,

968
00:31:01,540 --> 00:31:01,880
 toplo.

969
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,100
 Isuse.

970
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:07,660
 Probajte taj drugi korak.

971
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:11,000
 Oprosti nekome.

972
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:14,900
 I zamoli nek se tebi oprosti.

973
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:16,820
 Dakle, odreći se zla.

974
00:31:16,820 --> 00:31:18,600
 Kako bi u tebe ušlo dobro,

975
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,240
 kako bi tvoje oči, duše,

976
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:22,060
 postale sposobne vidjeti Boga.

977
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:25,080
 I odluči da ćeš biti pošten,

978
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,340
 da više nećeš psovati,

979
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:27,520
 da nećeš krasti,

980
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,820
 da nećeš ogovarati.

981
00:31:28,820 --> 00:31:31,300
 Vidjet ćeš kako tebi rase sposobnost.

982
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:39,240
 Boga se vidi na putovima sunca,

983
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:41,280
 pravde, dobrote, ljudskosti,

984
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,280
 humanosti,

985
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:44,540
 čovjekoljubivosti.

986
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:45,180
 Samo tu.

987
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:48,180
 U mržnika ne možeš vidjeti.

988
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,080
 Mržnja je mrak,

989
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,200
 ogovaranje je mrak,

990
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,160
 krađa je mrak,

991
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,220
 psovka je mrak,

992
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:52,900
 bludnost.

993
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:55,160
 I tako dalje,

994
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,500
 pravdub je mrak.

995
00:31:56,500 --> 00:31:59,900
 Tu Boga ne možeš vidjeti.

996
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:02,620
 Samo se odlučio,

997
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:03,700
 hoću biti pošten.

998
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,420
 Žao mi je.

999
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:08,840
 Zašto desni razbojnik je vidio Isusa

1000
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:09,640
 i da je on Bog?

1001
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,960
 Ljevi to nije vidio.

1002
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,300
 Ja desni je rekao,

1003
00:32:12,300 --> 00:32:12,900
 gospodine,

1004
00:32:12,900 --> 00:32:13,860
 žao mi je,

1005
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:14,960
 ja sam grešnik.

1006
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:17,020
 Ja sam kriv što sam,

1007
00:32:17,020 --> 00:32:18,740
 ja sam zaslužio da sam na križu,

1008
00:32:18,740 --> 00:32:19,580
 ali ti si nevin.

1009
00:32:19,580 --> 00:32:21,400
 Žao mi je,

1010
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,480
 Isuse, sjeti me se,

1011
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,160
 oprosti mi.

1012
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,500
 A ono je desni vikao,

1013
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:26,040
 stavi, skiniti nas križa

1014
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:26,520
 i ovo ono je,

1015
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:29,020
 kaže, pa nisam te ni stavio na križ,

1016
00:32:29,020 --> 00:32:29,700
 šta ćete skiniti?

1017
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:34,540
 Vidite koliko je različite.

1018
00:32:34,540 --> 00:32:35,940
 Ovaj desni je zapravo

1019
00:32:35,940 --> 00:32:37,400
 se uspao na razinu duha,

1020
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,260
 oprosti mi.

1021
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:39,860
 I mogo je prepoznati

1022
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:40,640
 Isusu da je Bog.

1023
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,820
 Ovaj ljeve,

1024
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:43,220
 misli samo na svoje životinsko.

1025
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:44,320
 deti me ne skini iz križa,

1026
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,140
 da da je nešto pojedem

1027
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:46,320
 i popijem i točka.

1028
00:32:46,320 --> 00:32:48,400
 Bi je na razini

1029
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,380
 psihofizičkoj,

1030
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:51,580
 a to je životinska razlina.

1031
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:52,320
 I životinje imaju

1032
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:53,400
 psihofizičku razlina

1033
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,060
 i zato ni mogu

1034
00:32:54,060 --> 00:32:56,360
 prepoznati Isusa kao Boga.

1035
00:32:56,360 --> 00:33:01,700
 Ajde, probajte.

1036
00:33:01,700 --> 00:33:02,820
 Odlučite se za dobro.

1037
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:04,340
 Vidite kako dobijate nove oči.

1038
00:33:05,340 --> 00:33:07,340
 i kako se i vaše zdravlje

1039
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:09,680
 od jednog puta rehabilitira.

1040
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:14,760
 Ako vam ne idete,

1041
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:16,120
 vi se opet vratite na ruku

1042
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:16,600
 pa pogledate.

1043
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:17,280
 Ah, tu si.

